Description:
    Creates a full Lesli vue application

Example:
    rails generate lesli:vue Core/Things
    rails generate lesli:vue CloudEngine/Things

    This will create:

        vue files:
            /engines/CloudEngine/lib/vue/apps/things/components/form.vue
            /engines/CloudEngine/lib/vue/apps/things/index.vue
            /engines/CloudEngine/lib/vue/apps/things/show.vue
            /engines/CloudEngine/lib/vue/apps/things/new.vue

        store:
            /engines/CloudEngine/lib/vue/apps/stores/things.js
